<div class="wrap"><div class="legal">
  <div class="note"><b>⚠ Placeholder</b> — Generate the final version with Shopify's free policy generator and have it reviewed before launch. The delivery windows below must match reality (FTC transparency rule).</div>

  <h2>Processing time</h2>
  <p>Orders are processed and dispatched within 1–2 business days. You'll receive a tracking number by email as soon as your order ships.</p>

  <h2>Delivery time</h2>
  <p>Delivery to the United States typically takes 8–15 days after dispatch. Delivery windows are estimates and can vary during peak periods and holidays. The estimated window is shown on the product page and again at checkout.</p>

  <h2>Shipping cost</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Free standard US shipping on orders over $35.</li>
    <li>Orders under $35: flat-rate shipping calculated at checkout.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Tracking</h2>
  <p>Every order ships with tracking. If your tracking hasn't updated within 5 business days of dispatch, contact us and we'll look into it.</p>

  <h2>Returns</h2>
  <p>We accept returns on unused items in original condition within 30 days of delivery. To start a return, email us with your order number. Return shipping is the customer's responsibility unless the item arrived damaged or incorrect.</p>

  <h2>Damaged or wrong item</h2>
  <p>If your order arrives damaged or isn't what you ordered, email us within 7 days of delivery with a photo and we'll make it right at no cost to you.</p>

  <h2>Refunds</h2>
  <p>Approved refunds are issued to the original payment method within 5–10 business days of us receiving the returned item. See our <a href="refund.html" style="color:var(--persimmon);text-decoration:underline">Refund Policy</a> for details.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions about an order? Reach us via the <a href="contact.html" style="color:var(--persimmon);text-decoration:underline">contact page</a>.</p>
